description:
## Ant Commander Pro - Professional file manager

![Screenshot of Ant Commander Pro](https://www.antcommander.com/images/ant-commander-pro-screenshot.png)

Ant Commander is a powerful file manager.

Several file systems are suported: file, zip, ftp, webdav, ftps, sftp, lst, tar.gz, etc.

Several kinds of panels are available: directory table, directory tree, text editor, image viewer, command line, etc.

Several file operation are supported: copy, move, delete, multiple rename, create directory, zip, unzip, etc.

And more: skinnable, OS independent, bookmarks, historic, a lot of file operations, etc.

Free to try for one day.
author: Japplis
